rows.label: tlk401004_msg0001
rows.name: Oh, I have a good one for you.

rows.label: tlk401004_msg0002
rows.name:
Some kind of ingredients with a
monstrously foul odor were carried
into the Superbian Divine Beast vessel.

rows.label: tlk401004_msg0003
rows.name:
The stench was so strong, I can
still smell it on my clothes.

rows.label: tlk401004_msg0004
rows.name:
There were other ingredients, too.
Weird and wonderful, the lot of them.

rows.label: tlk401004_msg0005
rows.name:
I don't know what they're for, but
it can't be your average recipes.
